  "title": "A round multicolor UFO was seen flying slow in Santa Cruz do Sul-RS [1996]",
  "URL": "http://brazilianufoarchives.com/2020/06/29/a-round-multicolor-ufo-was-seen-flying-slow-in-santa-cruz-do-sul-rs-1996/",
  "short_URL": "https://wp.me/pc3ctW-1eT",
  "content": "<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><strong>MARCH 20th, 1996</strong>. Time: 19h30. Duration: ongoing during the report. On a night of clear sky and good visibility, an entire neighborhood in the city of Santa Cruz do Sul, State of Rio Grande do Sul, observed a UFO with a round shape, &#8220;three times the size of a star&#8221; as seen in the sky. According to the witnesses, the unidentified flying object was multicolored and flew with a slow speed and at a high altitude. The UFO was sighted in the western direction of the city, following a straight path parallel to the horizon.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>Cf.</em> ARQUIVO NACIONAL (Brasil). Sistema de Informações do Arquivo Nacional (SIAN). Fundo ‘Objeto Voador Não Identificado (OVNI)’. Código de Referência BR DFANBSB ARX.0.0.412. “</span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">Questionário sobre a ocorrência de objeto voador na região de Santa Cruz do Sul, Estado do Rio Grande do Sul”. Brasília, DF. 1952 a 2015. Último acesso realizado em 27/05/2020.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align:justify;\"><em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\">The BRAZILIAN UFO ARCHIVES website is a private initiative and IS NOT endorsed or sponsored by the Arquivo Nacional do Brasil [see our ‘Info’ page]. </span></em><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"><em>*THE ORIGINAL FILE WITH THE CASE REFERRED TO IN THIS TEXT CAN BE FOUND IN THE DOCUMENTAL COLLECTION OF “ARQUIVO NACIONAL DO BRASIL, LOCATED IN THE “OBJETO VOADOR NÃO IDENTIFICADO (OVNI)” FUND, UNDER THE REFERENCE CODE [“Código de Referência”] MENTIONED ABOVE.</em> <strong><a style=\"color:#808000;\" href=\"http://sian.an.gov.br/sianex/consulta/login.asp\">HERE IS THE LINK TO SEARCH THEIR WEBSITE</a></strong></span><span style=\"font-family:Verdana;font-size:small;color:#808000;\"> </span>&lt;</p>\n",
  "excerpt": "<p>MARCH 20th, 1996. Time: 19h30. Duration: ongoing during the report. On a night of clear sky and good visibility, an entire neighborhood in the city of Santa Cruz do Sul, State of Rio Grande do Sul, observed a UFO with a round shape, &#8220;three times the size of a star&#8221; as seen in the sky. [&hellip;]</p>\n",
